            .paragraph
                p Cowboy Art specializes in outdoor advertising, vehicle branding, and the creation of all types of commercial signage. Over the years, the studio has completed more than 7,000 projects.
                p However, the current website is outdated and does not reflect the full range of services the company now offers. The goal of the new website is to expand the list of services, improve navigation, and present the company in a modern and engaging format.

